description: This Chainlink VRF common Yulenka purrs with a rating of 52, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 52, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, Box for East, 1 for South, and 3 for West. Yulenka has the personality suit of yenta. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/80521-74134-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Yulenka [52 Votes, Common]
